## 2. Acceptance criteria

- [ ] `uv run uvicorn main:app --reload` boots cleanly; `/healthz` returns 200
- [ ] Every route has a Pydantic request + response model (no `dict[str, Any]`)
- [ ] `uv run pytest` is green
- [ ] `uv run ruff check` and `uv run pyright` (or `mypy --strict`) are green
- [ ] OpenAPI spec at `/docs` lists every public route

## 3. Non-goals

- No synchronous endpoints — embrace `async def`
- No raw SQL or pickled state — use a typed driver (asyncpg, redis-py)
- No global state — per-request dependency injection via `Depends`

